headline: Kroger Earns Bell Seal for Workplace Mental Health for Fourth Consecutive Year
summary: The Kroger Co. (NYSE: KR), America's grocer, today announced it has been awarded the 2025 Gold Bell Seal for Workplace Mental Health. The Bell Seal program from Mental Health America (MHA) is a first-of-its-kind workplace certification that recognizes employers who strive to create mentally healthy workplaces for their associates.
